description: Returns a list of objects that contain information about events in a flow execution.

parameters.name: flowExecutionId
parameters.description: The ID of the flow execution.

nested_items.name: messages
nested_items.description: A list of objects that contain information about events in the specified flow execution.

nested_items.name: messageId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier of the message.

nested_items.name: timestamp
nested_items.description: The date and time when the message was last updated.

nested_items.name: payload
nested_items.description: A string containing information about the flow event.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: The string to specify as nextToken when you request the next page of results.
